House salted chunky Fritz Fries & soft drink.

item.title: Bookings
item.dc:creator: sam.muir@tower.co.nz
item.content:encoded:
Running an awesome function is complicated, we get that. So let us handle the function catering for you. Every event is different, and that’s why we’re flexible enough to work our wiener catering in with your needs.
Got a heap of people to feed? We can send more than one truck! Dietary requirements? We’ve got those covered. Something for the kids? No problem. More questions? Just get in touch.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value:
Weddings

Looking for some non traditional wedding catering? Then a food truck is the perfect option for you. Skip the sit down dinner and let your guests grab arguable the best wiener in the world from us. Your guests will love spending more time dancing and less time passing the salad to your crazy uncle Mick.

Corporate bookings

Throw out the cucumber sandwiches and tell the office manager that there will be no cold platters at this years EOFY party. Not on your watch. Become a true office legend and lock in Mr Burger for your next Christmas bash, end of project party or team bonding session.

Private bookings

Are you about to launch the next Instagram? Opening a gallery? Have you just made something really cool that you want to tell everyone about? We’re excited! Let’s throw a party. We’ve got the food covered, hell we can even sort out the booze. Let us take care of the catering, so you can spend more time working that crowd. Your guests will love having something they can eat with one hand on the move… No table required!

Birthdays

Book us for your birthday, and the only thing you’ll have to worry about is knocking back gate crasher's when they find out your old mate Fritz is going to be there. 18th's, 21st's, 30th's, even 100th birthdays. You're never too old to have a Wiener on your special day.

item.title: About us
item.dc:creator: sam.muir@tower.co.nz
item.content:encoded:
• 2004 - The beginning
    Fritz’s was dreamed up over a few beers between Bryan Stenning, a radio marketing executive and Todd Heller one of New Zealand’s best butchers. The idea was conceived and in late 2004 Fritz’s did their first ever event. The product was a hit!
  • 2009 - Franchising
    After proof of concept was achieved it was time to spread the wieners far and wide. Our first franchisee started in Auckland in late 2009.
  • 2014 - Crossing the ditch
    In 2014 we were invited to arguably one of Australia’s most prestigious motor racing events the Bathurst 1000. Sourcing a local producer of our awarding winning sausages and establishing the brand in Australia.
  • 2018 – Franchisees all around the country
    With new franchisees in Hamilton and Queenstown you can now find us the length of the country popping up at your favourite events.
  • 2019 - Restaurant opening
    New restaurant opening in the new River Side market in the Christchurch CBD.
  • 2020- Kombi Van launched in Dundein
  • Now
    Today you can find Fritz at the s the largest events in New Zealand as well weekly markets and private functions. We are also open in fixed locations in Northland, Wellington and Christchurch.

item.title: Franchising / Licensing
item.dc:creator: sam.muir@tower.co.nz
item.content:encoded:
The Fritz’s model is based on product licensing. The initial cost is based on your start equipment.
If you would like to know more about joining the Fritz Family, just get in touch.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: #1IT’S SO SIMPLE! We supply you with our award winning sausages, a custom built roller grill than can withstand selling thousands of sausages with ease, over an open flame and the systems to pump out product fast, when it counts!

#2EXTRA EQUIPMENT You’re not confined to just one setup. We understand that not all events are created equal and because of this we have multiple types of setups to suit every requirement so you can customise your business to suit your needs. Fritz Kombi, Fritz Hut, Mini Fritz and bricks n Mortar.

#3CORPORATE SUPPORT We understand that your ultimate success is our success, so we help you every step of the way. With a combined 30 years management experience in the mobile events space you can be sure that we know what we are doing.
#4ESTABLISHED BRAND With 16 years in the industry and representation in Australia and the length of New Zealand. Fritz’s Wieners is a well-developed and respected brand in our category.

#5EXTREMELY QUICK START UP We’ll have you up and running in under 60 days from signing*. We know that when you decide to go into business for yourself, you don’t want to wait years to make that dream a reality.

Mini Fritz

Features:
  • Fully branded commercial grade Marquee - Helping you stand out!
  • High output commercial grill.
  • Custom-built stainless-steel sausage rotisserie.
  • Supplied with full council compliance so you can start trading and making money fast!
  • Suited to local markets, fetes, private functions, events.
This includes your Mini Fritz setup and everything you need to start trading at your local market or event. You will need a vehicle capable of towing a standard domestic size trailer (under 750KG)

Kombi Style Fritz

Features:
  • Fully wrapped Kombi Style Van (not road legal).
  • Compact full stainless-steel kitchen.
  • High output commercial grill.
  • Custom-built stainless-steel sausage rotisserie.
  • Supplied with full council compliance so you can start trading and making money fast!
Suited to markets, fetes, parties, weddings, festivals, events

Custom Built Fritz Hut

This is for the experienced pros, designed exactly to your requirements. Built in Australia. You will work directly with our trailer manufactures (with our help, if you need of course!) to get exactly what you need to maximize your sales and profitability. Features:
  • Our own customised suspension system allowing the trailer to kneel to the ground during service.
  • Removable drawbar.
  • Full stainless steel custom designed interior.
  • High output commercial grill.
  • Custom built stainless sausage rotisserie.
  • Full signage wrap.
  • Large Rooftop sign.
  • Supplied with full council compliance so you can start trading and making money fast!
Suited to markets, fetes, parties, weddings, festivals, Large scale events, Stadiums, Motor racing basically anywhere where there’s a lot of hungry people.

item.title: Locations
item.dc:creator: sam.muir@tower.co.nz
item.content:encoded:
Fritz's Wieners are located all around New Zealand. We have mobile locations in Auckland, Hamilton, Wellington, Christchruch and Dunedin, and also a store front in Paihia.

Want your location here? Contact us to see how you can join the Fritz family.
